### 16. AnalyzeInflationImpact

**Steps**: purely illustrative purchasing-power erosion calculation using the same inflation assumption as above → recommend TIPS (Treasury Inflation-Protected Securities) allocation within the bond sleeve as the standard inflation-hedging instrument for the portion of the portfolio meant to fund essential (non-discretionary) retirement spending — this is well-established fixed-income practice, not a novel recommendation.

