## Appendix: Generic Confidence Formula (fallback only)

`confidence = 0.85 × (1 − 0.01 × years_to_horizon) × input_completeness_factor`, floored at `0.3`. As with the other two agent files, every skill above defines its own formula deliberately — this fallback exists only for genuinely novel skills added after this document's last verification date, and should trigger a documentation-update task rather than being relied upon long-term.
